name: DYSTOPIA:ZOEY
description: She is the princess of her race. When Zoey was young she was taught self defense and she has a prolific shooting. Her father never wanted her to be his heir-to-the-throne. She is a rebel. Zoey has an terrible allergy to dust and her father lied about it. He said to her that she was going to die young because she had a terminal illness. She left the palace to never come back when she discovered THE TRUTH.
